Summary: Nothing like I have ever seen in my life.
divs: Sighting DetailsAt the time I was at the park walking around. I first noticed the object when I heard loud buzzing. I honestly don't know. It amazed me.. Nothing like I have ever seen before, but I think somehow it knew I saw it. It was moving then it stopped for awhile. My vision was going blurry, went dizzy, and my head started hurting around 5 minutes after observing it. It flew away astonishingly fast.
